    exact_mod_cast hp
```

Similarly for $d$:

```tactics
  have hd' : (d : ℝ) = 1 / 2 * ∑ i, ∑ j ∈ (Finset.univ \ {i - 1, i, i + 1}), dist (P i) (P j) := by
    exact_mod_cast hd
```

Now we have $p'$ and $d'$ as real numbers.

